long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
View Discord's user ID and token information.

# How to use
1. Open discord.com and log in to the application
2. Open the extension
3. Check the options you want to see on the extension
4. Click to view

# Feature
✓ View the list of UserId, Token, etc.
✓ Completely free.
✓ Safe and secure, no information is collected.

# Modified
Fix some bug
